Package: request
Title: High Level 'HTTP' Client
Description: High level and easy 'HTTP' client for 'R' that makes assumptions
    that should work in most cases. Provides functions for building 'HTTP'
    queries, including query parameters, body requests, headers, authentication,
    and more.
Version: 0.1.5.9210
Authors@R: person("Scott", "Chamberlain", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "myrmecocystus@gmail.com")
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/sckott/request
BugReports: https://github.com/sckott/request/issues
Depends:
    httr (>= 1.2.0)
Imports:
    methods,
    stats,
    utils,
    curl (>= 2.2),
    jsonlite (>= 1.1),
    magrittr (>= 1.5),
    lazyeval (>= 0.2.0),
    whisker (>= 0.3-2),
    R6 (>= 2.2.0),
    tibble (>= 1.2),
    digest,
    rappdirs
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr,
    data.table
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
